name: ProtoPie UI Kit
description:
The ProtoPie UI Kit helps you turn your Figma designs into highly interactive prototypes for the first time.


Whatâ€™s included?

  • Instructions on how to use the ProtoPie plugin for Figma.
  • Tips on how you can learn ProtoPie step by step.
  • UI assets used in the ProtoPie workshops that you can use to create your first interactive prototypes.


Feel free to use the UI assets alongside the ProtoPie workshops (links in the file) and add powerful interactions to your Figma designs.


Use conditions, text input, camera, voice, and a whole lot more to take your Figma designs to the next level. The possibilities are endless.


The ProtoPie plugin for Figma requires you to use ProtoPie 5.2 or higher.
